            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3ESociety's%20hatred%20for%20the%20Jews%20has%20always%20been%20extreme%20and%20inexplicable.%20The%20magnitude%20of%20their%20suffering%20defies%20reason.%20The%20fact%20remains%2C%20however%2C%20that%20Satan%20knew%20salvation%20(Jesus)%20would%20come%20from%20the%20Jews%2C%20and%20thus%20he%20sought%20at%20every%20turn%20to%20destroy%20the%20Jewish%20people.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20Jews'%20worship%20of%20the%20true%20God%20and%20their%20rejection%20of%20idolatry%20led%20Mordecai%20to%20refuse%20to%20worship%20any%20human%20being%20(Esther%203%3A5).%20Haman's%20well-conceived%20plot%20looked%20foolproof%2C%20but%20God%20had%20been%20engineering%20a%20rescue%20operation%20about%20which%20Haman%20knew%20nothing.%20Working%20her%20way%20up%20to%20the%20right%20hand%20of%20the%20king%20was%20a%20little%20orphan%20(Esther)%2C%20who%20would%20ultimately%20be%20the%20tool%20of%20deliverance%20in%20the%20hand%20of%20God.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ESatan%20is%20enraged%20by%20anyone%20who%20refuses%20to%20bow%20down%20and%20worship%20him%2C%20and%20he%20will%20do%20whatever%20he%20can%20to%20destroy%20such%20a%20person.%20%20Satan's%20best%20plans%2C%20however%2C%20are%20no%20match%20for%20God%2C%20who%20knows%20the%20end%20from%20the%20beginning%20and%20the%20%22way%20out%22%20of%20the%20problem%20before%20the%20%22way%20in%22%20even%20existed!%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EStand%20still%20and%20wait%20on%20God%2C%20for%20He%20has%20known%20the%20solution%20to%20your%20problem%20since%20before%20it%20came%20into%20existence!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
            "id": "ot-passage",
            "type": "passage",
            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Esther.1:1-3:15",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EEsther%201%3A1-3%3A15%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_1_1%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EEsther%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20King%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Banquet%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThese%20events%20happened%20in%20the%20days%20of%20King%20Xerxes%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E1%3A1a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EAhasuerus%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20another%20name%20for%20Xerxes%3B%20also%20throughout%20the%20book%20of%20Esther.%20Xerxes%20reigned%20486%26%23x2013%3B465%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-sc%22%3Eb.c.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20who%20reigned%20over%20127%26%23xA0%3Bprovinces%20stretching%20from%20India%20to%20Ethiopia.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E1%3A1b%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Eto%20Cush.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_1_2%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EAt%20that%20time%20Xerxes%20ruled%20his%20empire%20from%20his%20royal%20throne%20at%20the%20fortress%20of%20Susa.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_1_3%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20the%20third%20year%20of%20his%20reign%2C%20he%20gave%20a%20banquet%20for%20all%20his%20nobles%20and%20officials.%20He%20invited%20all%20the%20military%20officers%20of%20Persia%20and%20Media%20as%20well%20as%20the%20princes%20and%20nobles%20of%20the%20provinces.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_1_4%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20celebration%20lasted%20180%26%23xA0%3Bdays%26%23x2014%3Ba%20tremendous%20display%20of%20the%20opulent%20wealth%20of%20his%20empire%20and%20the%20pomp%20and%20splendor%20of%20his%20majesty.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_1_5%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20it%20was%20all%20over%2C%20the%20king%20gave%20a%20banquet%20for%20all%20the%20people%2C%20from%20the%20greatest%20to%20the%20least%2C%20who%20were%20in%20the%20fortress%20of%20Susa.%20It%20lasted%20for%20seven%20days%20and%20was%20held%20in%20the%20courtyard%20of%20the%20palace%20garden.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_1_6%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20courtyard%20was%20beautifully%20decorated%20with%20white%20cotton%20curtains%20and%20blue%20hangings%2C%20which%20were%20fastened%20with%20white%20linen%20cords%20and%20purple%20ribbons%20to%20silver%20rings%20embedded%20in%20marble%20pillars.%20Gold%20and%20silver%20couches%20stood%20on%20a%20mosaic%20pavement%20of%20porphyry%2C%20marble%2C%20mother-of-pearl%2C%20and%20other%20costly%20stones.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_1_7%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EDrinks%20were%20served%20in%20gold%20goblets%20of%20many%20designs%2C%20and%20there%20was%20an%20abundance%20of%20royal%20wine%2C%20reflecting%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20generosity.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_1_8%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EBy%20edict%20of%20the%20king%2C%20no%20limits%20were%20placed%20on%20the%20drinking%2C%20for%20the%20king%20had%20instructed%20all%20his%20palace%20officials%20to%20serve%20each%20man%20as%20much%20as%20he%20wanted.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_1_9%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Queen%20Vashti%20gave%20a%20banquet%20for%20the%20women%20in%20the%20royal%20palace%20of%20King%20Xerxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_1_10%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EQueen%20Vashti%20Deposed%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EOn%20the%20seventh%20day%20of%20the%20feast%2C%20when%20King%20Xerxes%20was%20in%20high%20spirits%20because%20of%20the%20wine%2C%20he%20told%20the%20seven%20eunuchs%20who%20attended%20him%26%23x2014%3BMehuman%2C%20Biztha%2C%20Harbona%2C%20Bigtha%2C%20Abagtha%2C%20Zethar%2C%20and%20Carcas%26%23x2014%3B%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_1_11%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3Eto%20bring%20Queen%20Vashti%20to%20him%20with%20the%20royal%20crown%20on%20her%20head.%20He%20wanted%20the%20nobles%20and%20all%20the%20other%20men%20to%20gaze%20on%20her%20beauty%2C%20for%20she%20was%20a%20very%20beautiful%20woman.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_1_12%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20when%20they%20conveyed%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20order%20to%20Queen%20Vashti%2C%20she%20refused%20to%20come.%20This%20made%20the%20king%20furious%2C%20and%20he%20burned%20with%20anger.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_1_13%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20immediately%20consulted%20with%20his%20wise%20advisers%2C%20who%20knew%20all%20the%20Persian%20laws%20and%20customs%2C%20for%20he%20always%20asked%20their%20advice.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_1_14%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20names%20of%20these%20men%20were%20Carshena%2C%20Shethar%2C%20Admatha%2C%20Tarshish%2C%20Meres%2C%20Marsena%2C%20and%20Memucan%26%23x2014%3Bseven%20nobles%20of%20Persia%20and%20Media.%20They%20met%20with%20the%20king%20regularly%20and%20held%20the%20highest%20positions%20in%20the%20empire.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_1_15%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BWhat%20must%20be%20done%20to%20Queen%20Vashti%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20the%20king%20demanded.%20%26%23x201C%3BWhat%20penalty%20does%20the%20law%20provide%20for%20a%20queen%20who%20refuses%20to%20obey%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20orders%2C%20properly%20sent%20through%20his%20eunuchs%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_1_16%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EMemucan%20answered%20the%20king%20and%20his%20nobles%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BQueen%20Vashti%20has%20wronged%20not%20only%20the%20king%20but%20also%20every%20noble%20and%20citizen%20throughout%20your%20empire.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_1_17%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EWomen%20everywhere%20will%20begin%20to%20despise%20their%20husbands%20when%20they%20learn%20that%20Queen%20Vashti%20has%20refused%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20king.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_1_18%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EBefore%20this%20day%20is%20out%2C%20the%20wives%20of%20all%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20nobles%20throughout%20Persia%20and%20Media%20will%20hear%20what%20the%20queen%20did%20and%20will%20start%20treating%20their%20husbands%20the%20same%20way.%20There%20will%20be%20no%20end%20to%20their%20contempt%20and%20anger.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_1_19%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BSo%20if%20it%20please%20the%20king%2C%20we%20suggest%20that%20you%20issue%20a%20written%20decree%2C%20a%20law%20of%20the%20Persians%20and%20Medes%20that%20cannot%20be%20revoked.%20It%20should%20order%20that%20Queen%20Vashti%20be%20forever%20banished%20from%20the%20presence%20of%20King%20Xerxes%2C%20and%20that%20the%20king%20should%20choose%20another%20queen%20more%20worthy%20than%20she.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_1_20%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20this%20decree%20is%20published%20throughout%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20vast%20empire%2C%20husbands%20everywhere%2C%20whatever%20their%20rank%2C%20will%20receive%20proper%20respect%20from%20their%20wives!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_1_21%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20king%20and%20his%20nobles%20thought%20this%20made%20good%20sense%2C%20so%20he%20followed%20Memucan%26%23x2019%3Bs%20counsel.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_1_22%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20sent%20letters%20to%20all%20parts%20of%20the%20empire%2C%20to%20each%20province%20in%20its%20own%20script%20and%20language%2C%20proclaiming%20that%20every%20man%20should%20be%20the%20ruler%20of%20his%20own%20home%20and%20should%20say%20whatever%20he%20pleases.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E1%3A22%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Eand%20should%20speak%20in%20the%20language%20of%20his%20own%20people.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_2_1%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EEsther%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EEsther%20Becomes%20Queen%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20after%20Xerxes%26%23x2019%3B%20anger%20had%20subsided%2C%20he%20began%20thinking%20about%20Vashti%20and%20what%20she%20had%20done%20and%20the%20decree%20he%20had%20made.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_2_2%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20his%20personal%20attendants%20suggested%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BLet%20us%20search%20the%20empire%20to%20find%20beautiful%20young%20virgins%20for%20the%20king.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_2_3%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3ELet%20the%20king%20appoint%20agents%20in%20each%20province%20to%20bring%20these%20beautiful%20young%20women%20into%20the%20royal%20harem%20at%20the%20fortress%20of%20Susa.%20Hegai%2C%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20eunuch%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20harem%2C%20will%20see%20that%20they%20are%20all%20given%20beauty%20treatments.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_2_4%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EAfter%20that%2C%20the%20young%20woman%20who%20most%20pleases%20the%20king%20will%20be%20made%20queen%20instead%20of%20Vashti.%26%23x201D%3B%20This%20advice%20was%20very%20appealing%20to%20the%20king%2C%20so%20he%20put%20the%20plan%20into%20effect.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_2_5%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EAt%20that%20time%20there%20was%20a%20Jewish%20man%20in%20the%20fortress%20of%20Susa%20whose%20name%20was%20Mordecai%20son%20of%20Jair.%20He%20was%20from%20the%20tribe%20of%20Benjamin%20and%20was%20a%20descendant%20of%20Kish%20and%20Shimei.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_2_6%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EHis%20family%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E2%3A6a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EHe.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20had%20been%20among%20those%20who%2C%20with%20King%20Jehoiachin%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E2%3A6b%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EJeconiah%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20variant%20spelling%20of%20Jehoiachin.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Judah%2C%20had%20been%20exiled%20from%20Jerusalem%20to%20Babylon%20by%20King%20Nebuchadnezzar.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_2_7%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20man%20had%20a%20very%20beautiful%20and%20lovely%20young%20cousin%2C%20Hadassah%2C%20who%20was%20also%20called%20Esther.%20When%20her%20father%20and%20mother%20died%2C%20Mordecai%20adopted%20her%20into%20his%20family%20and%20raised%20her%20as%20his%20own%20daughter.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_2_8%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EAs%20a%20result%20of%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20decree%2C%20Esther%2C%20along%20with%20many%20other%20young%20women%2C%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20harem%20at%20the%20fortress%20of%20Susa%20and%20placed%20in%20Hegai%26%23x2019%3Bs%20care.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_2_9%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EHegai%20was%20very%20impressed%20with%20Esther%20and%20treated%20her%20kindly.%20He%20quickly%20ordered%20a%20special%20menu%20for%20her%20and%20provided%20her%20with%20beauty%20treatments.%20He%20also%20assigned%20her%20seven%20maids%20specially%20chosen%20from%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20palace%2C%20and%20he%20moved%20her%20and%20her%20maids%20into%20the%20best%20place%20in%20the%20harem.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_2_10%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EEsther%20had%20not%20told%20anyone%20of%20her%20nationality%20and%20family%20background%2C%20because%20Mordecai%20had%20directed%20her%20not%20to%20do%20so.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_2_11%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EEvery%20day%20Mordecai%20would%20take%20a%20walk%20near%20the%20courtyard%20of%20the%20harem%20to%20find%20out%20about%20Esther%20and%20what%20was%20happening%20to%20her.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_2_12%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EBefore%20each%20young%20woman%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20bed%2C%20she%20was%20given%20the%20prescribed%20twelve%20months%20of%20beauty%20treatments%26%23x2014%3Bsix%20months%20with%20oil%20of%20myrrh%2C%20followed%20by%20six%20months%20with%20special%20perfumes%20and%20ointments.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_2_13%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20it%20was%20time%20for%20her%20to%20go%20to%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20palace%2C%20she%20was%20given%20her%20choice%20of%20whatever%20clothing%20or%20jewelry%20she%20wanted%20to%20take%20from%20the%20harem.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_2_14%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EThat%20evening%20she%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20private%20rooms%2C%20and%20the%20next%20morning%20she%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20second%20harem%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E2%3A14%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Eto%20another%20part%20of%20the%20harem.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20where%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20wives%20lived.%20There%20she%20would%20be%20under%20the%20care%20of%20Shaashgaz%2C%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20eunuch%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20concubines.%20She%20would%20never%20go%20to%20the%20king%20again%20unless%20he%20had%20especially%20enjoyed%20her%20and%20requested%20her%20by%20name.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22esth_2_15%22%20bk%3D%22esth%22%20ch%3D%222%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EEsther%20was%20the%20daughter%20of%20Abihail%2C%20who%20was%20Mordecai%26%23x2019%3Bs%20uncle.%20(Mordecai%20had%20adopted%20his%20younger%20cousin%20Esther.)%20When%20it%20was%20Esther%26%23x2019%3Bs%20turn%20to%20go%20to%20the%20king%2C%20she%20accepted%20the%20advice%20of%20Hegai%2C%20the%20eunuch%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20harem.%20She%20asked%20for%20nothing%20except%20what%20he%20suggested%2C%20and%20she%20was%20admired%20by%20everyone%20w